	Title: Release 20200503
	Author: Paul Chote
	Content: We are pleased to finally announce Release 20200503, which brings long-awaited UI improvements, core engine upgrades, and balance improvements:\n\n  • Smooth Zooming and UI size configuration\n  • New campaign missions for TD and D2k\n  • New Spectator Army tab\n  • New hotkeys for harvesters and factory selection\n  • Red Alert balance changes\n  • Undo/Redo support for the map editor\n  • More crash, bug, and performance fixes\n\nSee the full news post at www.openra.net for a patch spotlight video and the release download!
